Per the [http://dsl.vodafone.de/hilfe/files/vfksc/pdf/DSL-EasyBox803_Installationsanleitung_201006.pdf quick install guide], the default SSID is '''EasyBox XXXXXX'''. However, on an actual unit, the SSID pattern is '''EasyBox-XXXXXX''' :(not the last three octets of the BSSID, upper case letters). ===Wikis=== *[https://openwrt.org/toh/astoria/arv752dpw22 ARV752DPW22 on the '''OpenWrt''' wiki] *{{TechInfoDepot|Vodafone_DSL-EasyBox_803}} ===Forums=== *[http://www.dd-wrt.com/phpBB2/viewtopic.php?t=150188 803A on the '''DD-WRT''' forums] *[http://www.arcor-user-forum.de/easybox-803a-arv752dpw22-annex-a-firmware-4583/ ''Easybox 803A (arv752dpw22) Annex A firmware'' on ''ArcorUser'' forums] *[http://www.arcor-user-forum.de/neu-easybox-803-a-3192/ ''Neu : EasyBox 803'' on '''ArcorUserForum'''] :(some internal image pictures available to logged in users) ===Firmware=== *[ftp://ftp.dd-wrt.com/betas/2018/08-14-2018-r36596/vodafone_easybox_803/ ''803A'' on '''DD-WRT''' Downloads] ===Serial=== ====Pinout==== The pinout is noted on the '''OpenWrt''' Wiki entry and is echoed below..
